awards.text: Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 1 win & 18 nominations.

fullplot: Based on the autobiography of Gypsy Rose Lee, this made-for-TV movie-previously a Broadway smash and a 1962 film-depicts the life and times of a stripper and her domineering mother.
